    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly way to get around? This vehicle is priced to sell and perfect for someone who isn't afraid of a little elbow grease! While it definitely shows its age and will need some mechanical attention and TLC to get back to its best, it offers a great opportunity to own a vehicle at a fraction of the usual cost. Grab this bargain today and make it your own!",
