    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a solid daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings on the panels, and the paint has lost some of its original luster. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows clear signs of use, including some wear on the upholstery and minor stains on the carpet. Mechanically, it remains reliable and has been regularly maintained, though it lacks the refinements of a newer model. It\u2019s a practical choice for someone who prioritizes utility and value over a perfect appearance.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some fading in the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows signs of wear and some minor staining from regular use. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads and a tire rotation. It is a solid, functional car for someone needing dependable transportation at a reasonable price point.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
